---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | 7-Day Phật Thất Retreat at Bodh Gaya">
    <section class="max-w-4xl py-16 space-y-10">
        <div>
            <p class="mb-3 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-neutral-500">About</p>
            <h1 class="mb-6">7-Day Phật Thất Retreat at Bodh Gaya</h1>
            <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                This retreat will take place in Bodh Gaya, India, from
                <strong>December 28, 2026 to January 3, 2027</strong>, offering a precious opportunity to return to the sacred land of the Buddha for
                pilgrimage, spiritual practice, and the nourishment of inner peace.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl">
            <img src="/images/bodhgaya.jpg" alt="Bodh Gaya" class="h-full max-h-[420px] w-full object-cover" />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6">
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Purpose of the Retreat</h2>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    This is a rare opportunity for practitioners to return to the place where the Buddha attained enlightenment, and to live in an atmosphere of
                    serenity, mindfulness, chanting, meditation, and Dharma learning.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Practice Tradition</h2>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    The retreat follows the traditional <strong>Pure Land</strong> practice in combination with <strong>Chan meditation</strong>, helping
                    participants cultivate faith, inner stability, mindfulness, and spiritual depth.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50 p-6">
                <h2 class="mb-4">Optional 4-Day Pilgrimage</h2>
                <p class="leading-8 text-neutral-700">
                    Before the retreat, participants may join an optional pilgrimage from
                    <strong>December 24 to December 27, 2026</strong>, visiting sacred Buddhist sites such as Dungeshwari Cave, Sujata Stupa, Rajgir, Vulture
                    Peak, Nalanda, Vaishali, Sarnath, and more.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-2">
            <a href="/en/register" class="btn btn-lg rounded-2xl">Register</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
